|-----------|------------------------------|--------------------|----------|
| P3 RANSAC affine | 7-DOF under-determined | sxy + t_xy locked → 3-DOF | re-run with the locked-prior warm-start; only solve `(t_z, θ_residual)` and (when Stage B passed) verify against pinned sz |
